{"tid":604974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一周必看】 疑誤買凶宅蝕住走　撻定收場輸1球","createTime":"2018-03-25T08:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T08:44:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"de1c7e34de3062c08264d6492b399768d3f7062e","tid":604974,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T08:41:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180325/20342368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F20342368&d=oaWwkkh%2B5ILexk9J9XZkAwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=28bf1157\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F20342368&h=591c7f48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180325/20342368</a><br />\n<br />\n【一周必看】<br />\n疑誤買凶宅蝕住走　撻定收場輸1球<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n樓市瘋狂令二手市場一盤難求，凶宅也成搶手貨，但有市民疑誤購凶宅撻定收場，恐損手近100萬元。<br />\n<br />\n大埔新達廣場6座一個中層實用面積617方呎單位，去年12月以828萬元易手，呎價13,420元，較銀行估值平逾百萬元。土地註冊處資料顯示，上址去年12月簽定正式買賣合約，以828萬元連租約出售，惟上月已取消交易。根據買賣合約，買家在簽定正式買賣合約時已支付樓價10%定金，涉及82.8萬元。若是次交易涉及任何一方悔約，對方料有權沒收全數定金或賠定，再計及代理佣金，恐損手近100萬元。"},{"pid":"2135aabfc7bb6cb4f64fe5bb6d15389d2312c9ce","tid":604974,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T08:44:01.000Z","msg":"自住唔怕跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}